Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/25574/', '[1] "Product Information. Turalio (pexidartinib)." Daiichi Sankyo, Inc., Parsippany, NJ.[2] "Product Information. Turalio (pexidartinib)." Daiichi Sankyo, Inc., Parsippany, NJ.', 1767369485);
